<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.5">
<l>āṟṟa nalla vakaikāṭṭu mammāṉai yamarartam</l>
<l>mēṟṟai yellāp poruḷum virittāṉai yemmāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>māṟṟa mālai puṉaintētti nāḷu makiḻveytiṉēṉ</l>
<l>kāṟṟiṉ muṉṉaṅ kaṭuki viṉainōykaḷ kariyavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who shows way that are good for coping, the bull</l>
<l>of the celestials, him who discloses all meaning, our father,</l>
<l>decorating [and] praising him with a word garland I have attained daily delight,</l>
<l>while the pains of karma, before coming near like the wind, are [now] burned.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
